{"tid":337522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[霸氣]若被立會追討薪津 姚松炎考慮索償300萬顧問費","createTime":"2017-07-27T11:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T14:48:57.000Z","uid":33890,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59e4290ec9d6971d70d3e372040e9e84109b9cdb","tid":337522,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T11:25:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170727/57007944\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170727%2F57007944&d=ALUAnwbwHc4NfDmR6FIHkYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=bf6b7fe8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170727%2F57007944&h=fa9d93a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170727/57007944</a><br />\n出任建築、測量、規劃及園境界立法會議員9個多月的姚松炎，本身為中大地理與資源學系副教授，因熟悉業界內部運作及其本身專業，在立會工程撥款會議上，往往能指出一般議員難以發現的政府計錯數目、文件陳述失實等問題。早前包括姚在內的4名議員因宣誓案而被褫奪議員資格，星期五下午要向立會交還議員辦公室，目前有待立會行管會決定4人是需否交還薪津。若最終被追討薪津，姚松炎表示會考慮經民事訴訟，向立會索償約300萬元顧問費用。<br />\n<br />\n據《now》報道，姚任職議員9個月期間共申領約300萬元薪津，若被追討相關款項，他會考慮以合約法「按勞計酬」形式，向立會追討這段期間自己提供的顧問服務。  <br />\n對比嗰D哎契弟叫人唔好追佢地錢,真係有風骨得多,真係今屆最高質議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c1ed27fbe90f1b3b4249d4fe0a789e30eea2a7","tid":337522,"uid":26037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T11:34:23.000Z","msg":"如果立法會追佢數大概會追幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecfac0464ec97356abf767138020a92a6f8ea0ff","tid":337522,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:04:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170727/57007944\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170727%2F57007944&d=ALUAnwbwHc4NfDmR6FIHkYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=bf6b7fe8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.a